## Strata MCP Tools Reference

| Tool | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `search_history` | Full-text search across all indexed sessions |
| `find_solutions` | Solution-biased search for errors and problems |
| `semantic_search` | Vector search (requires GEMINI_API_KEY) |
| `get_project_context` | Recent sessions and key topics for a project |
| `get_session_summary` | Detailed summary of a specific session |
| `list_projects` | All projects with indexed history |
| `find_patterns` | Recurring topics, workflows, and issues |
| `store_memory` | Persist a decision, solution, or fact |
| `delete_memory` | Remove a stale memory entry |
